DialogueNode.dialogue: Hello Mr. Johnson. How are you doing today?
Ah, hello Alex. I'm doing great! How is your first week going?
Very good sir. I really think I'm getting along great with everyone.
Ok.... I think? I still feel a bit awkward around the other employees.
That's very good to hear. Getting along with the employees is your job technically speaking.
That's ok. You're still new around here. Sometimes it takes a little while to get adjusted.
Has anyone been giving you any trouble?
Has anyone been giving you any trouble?
Oh! Of course not. Everyone is wonderful and very welcoming. I couldn't be happier so far.
Not really. It could be... easier I guess but I've really enjoyed talking to everyone so far.
Not really... everyone just seems so close already. I don't want to butt in.
Janet seems a bit flighty I guess but I don't think there's any real problems there...
Stan kinda gives me the creeps to be honest.
That's great to hear! Well, I'd better get back to work. You should too. It was good talking to you Alex.
Well, that's something at least. I'm sure any uneasiness will pass though. I'd better get back to work. You should too. It was good talking to you Alex.
Oh nonsense. I'm sure they'd love to chat. We're like a family here at Big Byte. Don't be shy!
Oh? Janet is one of the nicest people I know. She works too hard though. She's probably just a bit busy.
Oh? Well. Stan is... a lot sometimes. He's a hard worker and a decent man though. Give him another chance for me will you?
Thank you sir! I'll do my best. I'd better get back to work. Thank you for talking with me.
Ah, that must be it. I'll go find her now! Thank you for talking with me sir.
Alright, I'll give it another go. Thank you for talking with me sir.
Anytime Alex!
